        	<h2>About WonderOps</h2>
             <div class="why-cho_inner_subtext"><img src="./images/hat-wand.jpg">

My name is Steve Lynch and I am in the Denver area. I am a failed entrepreneur. I tried a couple of times to get my own start up going, but I came to realize I always got caught up doing the things I liked least. WonderOps is what remains of my last attempt and when viewed in a different light is successful. It is a platform for my ability to help others with what I know through side work. What was once a source of stress and energy drain, now is a source of joy. 
<br><br>

I work in DevOps as my day job. I build software pipelines and automate. There is always much to learn. However, it is a domain within Information Technology that I genuinely enjoy. If you need some help, don't hesitate to reach out. I only work with small, flexible organizations. 
